If you’re looking to sell your home, you’re probably trying to decide whether to use a traditional real estate agent or sell it by yourself (FSBO).
How Real Estate Agents Get PaidReal estate agents get paid for their services through commissions.
But the listing agent — or the real estate agent who helps you sell your home — typically gets about half that amount.
There Are Alternate Ways To SellIn the age of online transactions, there are many alternate ways to sell your home, aside from the traditional real estate agent.
